    <p id="Par21">Operating system(s): Linux.</p>
    <p id="Par22">Programming language: Python 3.</p>
    <p id="Par23">Other requirements: pypi packages (argparse, biopython, configs, reportlab, pybedtools, wand, wheel), ImageMagick (OS-level requirement for wand).</p>
